(2. Core Teaching) Tj
T*
(The central focus in Data Structures is lists, stacks, queues, trees, and choosing the) Tj
T*
(right structure. This means students must move beyond the overview and understand how) Tj
T*
(the idea actually works. A strong explanation should unpack the rules, relationships, or) Tj
T*
(patterns behind Data Structures and show how those ideas guide correct answers. In) Tj
T*
(Computer Science, success usually depends on understanding the commands, structure, and) Tj
T*
(logic that belong to the topic.) Tj
